Design personalized hats for staff and family – unique, branded hats for all seasons.

Got a company logo, team badge or message that you want to add to custom caps? Our intuitive design studio makes it easy to create exactly what you have in mind.

Whether you’re ordering promotional hats for your whole team or creating something fun for friends and family, hats with your logo or monogram are popular products that get plenty of wear.

From custom text to business logos and club emblems, you can put almost anything on branded hats. Design your own hat to create a unique and united look for groups, teammates and colleagues. VistaPrint offers custom hats with no minimum order quantity – which makes them ideal for gifting.

Frequently Asked Questions

Your logo, photo or artwork is added onto your custom cap using either embroidery or heat transfer.

Yes. If you have a design ready to go, you’ll be able to upload it after you select your personalized cap color and quantity. We accept most common file types, including .pdf, .ai, .jpeg, .png, .doc and .ppt.

In the case of most branded hats and baseball caps, washing isn’t recommended. They may lose their shape and the design might get damaged.

Our heat transfer decoration technology lets you add photos that include as many colors as you need to. Embroidery is ideal for logos with up to 12 colors. Lastly, screen printing is great for 1-color designs.

Of course – you can design a hat and have it delivered. But the more custom caps with logo you buy, the less you pay per unit.
